name: Rami Babie
description: I am a very communicative, cheerful, with a good sense of humor. I am kind, attentive, vigorous and an optimist. I love children very much!I am positive and sociable woman who is looking for happiness. I enjoy nature, I get a lot of fun while listening to music, attending concerts and theatrical performances, art shows. I just love to get together with friends and joke with each other. Happiness and health of my family are the most important things for me. I am looking for an interesting person, A man with good manners and a big and very kind heart! The one I could wrap into a warm blanket with and sit on a cozy couch together, when it is a stormy weather outside and feel his warmth and care. The one who will appreciate me as a woman and my personality
